column5: anyone on here have any info on the big walleye tourney they have on this lake
They should have one next summer if the situation is stable or improving with covid19 They annonce it on their Facebook page
are there places to stay on this lake?

There is not many cottages on the lake and the one that are for renting for this event are rent to the same guys year after year. If tou want to know more you should contact the organizers they may be able to help you with this.
